As the kiss broke & he spoke to her, she groaned & hung her head. Just when 
she had returned to him, she had to go once more. & it was unknown when she 
would see him again. So much to do. 

"Indeed," her voice betrayed the sigh in it of needing to leave him, to deal 
with others. 

Her arms slid down, as a hand patted his upper chest near the shoulder. 
"Hevn, first ... & Blackstorm. What do you want done with Blackstorm?" She had 
taken a liking to her. Very few bots get the praise & liking from Maxima. 


--part1_190.1bedb727.2c1fe807_boundary
